{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_婆子",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·第一单（婆子上门）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "xg_pozi_done",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "npc" },
      "text": "小先生的恩，老婆子记下了。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "npc" },
      "text": "可算寻着了！你就是……李天狗那一脉的小先生不？",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "player" },
      "text": "（李天狗那一脉？……哦。俺。）正是。",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "npc" },
      "text": "俺家院里，夜夜有动静！鸡也不下蛋了，狗叫到后半夜——钱，老婆子拍这儿了！您可得给瞧瞧！",
      "next": "c1"
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「走。带俺去看。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        },
        {
          "id": "tai",
          "text": "〔抬抬价〕「这种活……寻常先生可不接。」",
          "next": "c_tai"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_tai": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "npc" },
      "text": "（一咬牙）再加十文！不能再多了，小先生！",
      "next": "c_tai_pay"
    },
    "c_tai_pay": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 10
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "c_jie": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "npc" },
      "text": "哎！哎！小先生这边走——",
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": { "kind": "literal", "name": "旁白" },
      "text": "这是头一个主动找上门的活儿。关二狗跟着婆子出城，一路把说书先生的词在肚子里又过了一遍。",
      "next": "n_go"
    },
    "n_go": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "婆子家院",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "entry"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
